### List all products from registry
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### Add laptop to Alice's cart
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cart/alice/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "LAPTOP-001",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Add keyboard to Alice's cart
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cart/alice/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "KB-002",
  "quantity": 2
}

### Add headphones to Alice's cart
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cart/alice/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "HP-005",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Get Alice's cart
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cart/alice

### Checkout Alice's cart (triggers delivery + email events)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cart/alice/checkout

### After checkout, cart is gone
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cart/alice

